    <section class="portal-section" id="contact">
        <div class="portal-section-header">
            <div class="portal-section-tag">FAQ</div>
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Everything you need to know about using MediCareMS effectively.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-faq">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" id="faq-q1" aria-expanded="false">
                    How do I book an appointment online?
                    <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-a1">
                    Click the <strong>Book Appointment</strong> button in the sidebar or on this page. Select your preferred department, choose a doctor, pick a date and time slot, then confirm your booking. You'll receive a confirmation with a unique appointment number and QR code.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" id="faq-q2" aria-expanded="false">
                    What insurance resources does MediCareMS accept?
                    <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-a2">
                    MediCareMS currently supports SSLCommerz online payment for consultation fees. We are actively working to integrate major health insurance providers. Please contact our support team for insurance-specific queries.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" id="faq-q3" aria-expanded="false">
                    How do I cancel my appointment?
                    <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-a3">
                    Navigate to <strong>My Appointments</strong> in the sidebar. Find your appointment and click the <strong>Cancel</strong> button. Cancellations can be made for appointments with Pending or Confirmed status. Completed appointments cannot be cancelled.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" id="faq-q4" aria-expanded="false">
                    Do you offer emergency medical services?
                    <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-a4">
                    Yes. For medical emergencies, please call our 24/7 hotline directly. You can also use the Aletta AI assistant on this page for immediate guidance. For life-threatening emergencies, please dial your local emergency services (999 in Bangladesh).
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" id="faq-q5" aria-expanded="false">
                    Can I get a digital prescription after my appointment?
                    <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-a5">
                    Yes. After your appointment is completed by the doctor, your digital prescription is available immediately under <strong>My Prescriptions</strong> in the sidebar. You can view it online anytime.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

